---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About TailPicked" description="We're the pet-obsessed friend who researches everything. Here's who we are and why we started TailPicked.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#7C3AED] to-[#9333EA] text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="bg-white/20 text-white text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1 rounded-full">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-users mr-2"></i>about
        </span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 font-['Fredoka'] text-white">About TailPicked</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-purple-100 max-w-2xl">
        We're the pet-obsessed friend who researches everything. Here's our story.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1F2937] mb-4 font-['Fredoka']">Picked with Love. Tested by Paws.</h2>
        <p class="text-[#6B7280] mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          We started TailPicked because we were tired of pet product reviews that felt like they were written by robots—or worse, by people who'd never actually owned a pet. You know the type: "This dog bed is great!" without mentioning that it falls apart after one wash.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#6B7280] mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          We're different. We're pet parents who <strong class="text-[#7C3AED]">actually test these products with our own pets</strong>. Every chew toy faces our power-chewing pit bull. Every litter box gets tested by our pickiest cat. If it doesn't hold up in our homes, we won't recommend it for yours.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1F2937] mb-4 mt-10 font-['Fredoka']">How We Test Products</h2>
        <p class="text-[#6B7280] mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Every product we recommend goes through real-world testing—not just a quick unboxing. We test for durability, safety, and whether pets actually like using them. Because a "top-rated" cat tree that your cat ignores isn't worth the cardboard it came in.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-[#FAF5FF] rounded-xl p-6 my-8 border border-purple-100">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#7C3AED] mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 font-['Fredoka']">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i> Our Promise to You (and Your Pets)
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-[#6B7280]">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#10B981] mt-1"></i>
              <span><strong class="text-[#1F2937]">Real pet testing</strong> — Products tested by actual dogs and cats</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#10B981] mt-1"></i>
              <span><strong class="text-[#1F2937]">Vet-reviewed</strong> — Veterinarians review our health recommendations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#10B981] mt-1"></i>
              <span><strong class="text-[#1F2937]">Safety first</strong> — We won't recommend anything we wouldn't give our own pets</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#10B981] mt-1"></i>
              <span><strong class="text-[#1F2937]">Honest ratings</strong> — If something sucks, we'll tell you</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-[#10B981] mt-1"></i>
              <span><strong class="text-[#1F2937]">Affiliate disclosure</strong> — We clearly mark affiliate links</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1F2937] mb-4 mt-10 font-['Fredoka']">Get in Touch</h2>
        <p class="text-[#6B7280] mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Want us to test a product? Have a question about pet care? Just want to send us cute pet pics? (Yes please!) We'd love to hear from you.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-[#6B7280]">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope text-[#7C3AED] w-6"></i>
            <span>hello@tailpicked.com</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-instagram text-[#7C3AED] w-6"></i>
            <span>@tailpicked</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-tiktok text-[#7C3AED] w-6"></i>
            <span>@tailpicked</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook text-[#7C3AED] w-6"></i>
            <span>facebook.com/tailpicked</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Meet the Team (Fun Version) -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-[#FAF5FF]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1F2937] mb-8 font-['Fredoka']">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-paw text-[#F59E0B] mr-2"></i> Our Testing Team
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[#6B7280] mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        The real experts behind TailPicked. They work for treats and belly rubs.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-purple-100">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#F59E0B] to-[#D97706] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-dog text-white text-3xl"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1F2937] font-['Fredoka']">Bruno</h3>
          <p class="text-[#7C3AED] text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Chief Chew Tester</p>
          <p class="text-[#6B7280] text-sm">If Bruno can't destroy it, it's truly indestructible.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-purple-100">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#7C3AED] to-[#9333EA] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-cat text-white text-3xl"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1F2937] font-['Fredoka']">Princess Luna</h3>
          <p class="text-[#7C3AED] text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Head of Quality Assurance</p>
          <p class="text-[#6B7280] text-sm">The pickiest cat alive. If she uses it, it's good.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-purple-100">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#10B981] to-[#059669] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-dog text-white text-3xl"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1F2937] font-['Fredoka']">Mochi</h3>
          <p class="text-[#7C3AED] text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Comfort Specialist</p>
          <p class="text-[#6B7280] text-sm">Our bed-testing expert. 18 hours of sleep daily.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
